title: Lombardi's Week 9 Watch List and the Dannys' Last-Second Fantasy Advice | GM Street (Ep. 336)
description:
The Ringer's Michael Lombardi and Tate Frazier discuss Jon Gruden’s lack of success in Oakland (01:30) before identifying the standout matchups this Sunday (14:30). Then Danny Heifetz and Danny Kelly of 'The Dantasy Football Podcast' dole out some fantasy football advice (32:45).
